direction: down

title: Distributed enforcement for agentic systems {
  style.font-size: 28
  style.font-color: "#e0e0e0"
  near: top-left
}
subtitle: Shared trust services produce signed decisions. Authoritative domains enforce them. Runtime containment catches what slips through. {
  style.font-size: 14
  style.font-color: "#858c85"
  near: top-left
}

